<br>
<br>
My question is.. What dropped this spell for you. Seriously. On Povar, you simply can't find it. We don't have people who play in SF.. Except necro solo ers. And we dont have anyone who does chardok, except for queen/king raids.<br>
<br>
-FallenDeity Decandidus- <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaeanorendarion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daeanor Endarion</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/picon.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/6/01 2:44:10 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/ppic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Draught of jiva, Who what where when how ?</span><hr size=1> A guildmate gave me my copy; I believe she picked up in Chardok on a royals raid. <p><table><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#cc0000 strength=1)><font size=2 color=#ffff00 face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Daeanor Endarion of the Rathe</font></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufanwenwiz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fanwen Wiz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/7/01 11:26:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Draught of jiva, Who what where when how ?</span><hr size=1> I recived this spell on chardok raid. Belive it dropped from a royal guard in the herbalist room. Good luck i know alot of wizards who still dont have this spell.<br>
